cheatSheet.commandDice.modelActivation=+1 model activation
cheatSheet.commandDice.modelActivation.desc=At the end of your model's activation, you may activate a second model

cheatSheet.commandDice.plusDice=+1 dice to any Shoot, Fight or Survive test
cheatSheet.commandDice.plusDice.desc=Add 1 dice to any Shoot, Fight or Survive test before rolling

cheatSheet.commandDice.additionalMove=Additional Move action
cheatSheet.commandDice.additionalMove.desc=The active model takes a free Move action. \
  This Move is restricted to one cube, regardless of the model's Speed stat, but otherwise follows the normal movement rules. \
  Can be used on models that have already taken a Move or Sprint action

cheatSheet.commandDice.additionalShoot=Additional Shoot action
cheatSheet.commandDice.additionalShoot.desc=The active model takes a free Shoot action. \
  Can be used on model that have already taken a Shoot action

cheatSheet.commandDice.additionalFight=Additional Fight action
cheatSheet.commandDice.additionalFight.desc=The active model takes a free Fight action. \
  May be used on models that have already taken a Fight action.

cheatSheet.commandDice.armySpecial=Army Special
cheatSheet.commandDice.armySpecial.desc=Activate your army's special ability. \
  The effect is different for each army and explained by the army list. \
  Army special effect do not count towards any other restriction on number of actions per turn unless specifically mentioned otherwise.
